{{Han etym}}
{{Han compound|ls=ic|匊|廾|alt2=𠬞|t1=rice in a house|t2=hands}} — to conceal and store rice in a house.<ref>鄔可晶《[https://web.archive.org/web/20250702144026/https://toaj.stpi.niar.org.tw/file/article/download/4b1141f9917320a501919237a3230a7d 釋“奥”]》2022年、『甲骨金文語文論稿』収録。</ref> {{och-l|*匊}} is unrelated to characters like {{och-l|*菊}}, which contain an abbreviated form of {{och-l|*鞠}} instead.

A conservative variant is [[𡪃]]. ''{{w|Shuowen}}'' interprets it as a {{Han compound|宀|𢍏|c1=s|c2=p|t1=roof|ls=psc}}, but is not widely accepted.

